defs.name: is_nullvector

attributes.value: / Tetermines whether or not the vector is the null-vector (0.,0.,0.)
/ let mut v: Vector3 = Vector3 { x: 0., y: 0., z: 0. };

defs.name: is_normalized

attributes.value: / tetermines whether or not the vector is normalized (of length 1)
/ let mut v: Vector3 = Vector3 { x: 0.75, y: 0.5, z: 0. };

defs.name: is_collinear

attributes.value: / tetermines whether or not one vector is a multiple of the other. Inputs must not be null-vectors
/ let v1: Vector3 = Vector3 { x: 0.75, y: 0.5, z: 6. };

defs.name: is_coplanar

attributes.value: / tetermines whether or not there exists a plane that contains all 3 vectors. Inputs must not be null-vectors
/ let mut v3 = Vector3 { x: 1., y: 0., z: -17. };
